incident_updates.body:
most of impacted services are now operational.
Our technical continue to work on resolving the issue.
Update will be post as significant progress is made.

Start time : 31/03/2023 22:00 UTC Root cause : Water cooling malfunction Ongoing actions : Our technical teams are hands on the issue. A lot of impacted services are operational anew. Update will be made as significant progress is made.

Investigation reported impact in racks R714B03, R714B02, R714B01, R714A05, R714A08, R714A16, and R714A15.
The issue is under control. Our technical teams are working on resolving the issue.
Update will be made as significant progress is made.
Start time : 31/03/2023 22:00 UTC Service impact : Some servers in the row R714 are down. Ongoing actions : Our teams are investigating to determine the origin of the incident and fix it.
